wesay (1.1.12-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * error reporting is now a separate app so should make reporting crashes easier
  * option to send error report by email can use thunderbird or
	   xdg-email which uses the default email program such as evolution or kmail
  * WS-34367 chorus not closing
  * change vb dependency to 10.0
  * most recently used projects now show in wesay config
  * WS-34372 detect USB properly and complain if more than 1
  * WS-34337 Get from USB and USB Send/receive should now work
  * add build-dep on libmono-addins-cil-dev - now using system one

 -- Daniel Glassey <daniel_glassey@sil.org>  Thu, 07 Jun 2012 14:37:49 +0700

